      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example delivers linear power through its individual throttle bodies, with the VANOS system recently overhauled for precise cam timing. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile shift throws, and the chassis remains rigid thanks to a proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The limited-slip differential operates silently, providing excellent torque vectoring out of corners. While the exterior shows honest road use consistent with its age, the drivetrain is optimized for performance, featuring healthy rod bearing clearances and a cooling system refreshed with a high-flow water pump. A technically sound driver\u2019s car for the purist who values mechanical integrity and throttle response.",
      "price": 32500.0,
